This is a description of how my codes work

TASK 1:
First it ask for input from the user usnig input function. with the input function i have added the float function because i needed to do the calculation in the code.
Here f_no refers to first number and s_no refers to second number.
Secondly it does the simple calculation with the recieved input. ie. addition, subtraction,  multiplication and division.
Lastly it shows the result in with help of print function.

TASK 2:
First it asks the user for its first and last name by using input function.
Here f_name refers to First name and s_name refers to last name.
Secondly it uses the recieved input to form a sentance. ie. Hello! (First name) (Last Name)! Welcome to the Python program.
